WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )


00:01:01.159 --> 00:01:01.840
Senior Brother

00:01:01.880 --> 00:01:02.880
Please, you must take me with you.

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:04.400
I can endure any hardship.

00:01:04.879 --> 00:01:06.000
Why endure hardship?

00:01:06.200 --> 00:01:08.239
You could have taken a private jet,

00:01:08.319 --> 00:01:09.959
a far comfier way to the Imperial Capital.

00:01:10.040 --> 00:01:11.439
But you chose a horse carriage instead,

00:01:11.439 --> 00:01:12.840
the most grueling way to travel.

00:01:13.480 --> 00:01:15.519
Though you said you came for the scenery,

00:01:15.879 --> 00:01:16.840
the way I see it,

00:01:17.439 --> 00:01:19.239
you really want to see the world,

00:01:19.719 --> 00:01:20.560
and find true freedom.

00:01:24.920 --> 00:01:25.719
Now I understand.

00:01:26.159 --> 00:01:27.079
Thank you for the guidance, Senior Brother.

00:01:27.840 --> 00:01:28.760
On the path of cultivation,

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:30.560
hardship is simply inevitable.

00:01:30.640 --> 00:01:32.280
If I keep treating it as suffering,

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:33.359
how could I ever move forward?

00:01:34.599 --> 00:01:36.959
I really regret not kicking you to death yesterday.

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:38.239
Senior Brother,

00:01:40.120 --> 00:01:40.920
that carriage over there,

00:01:41.359 --> 00:01:43.200
I had my company build it overnight.

00:01:44.359 --> 00:01:45.680
What an adorable carriage.

00:01:54.879 --> 00:01:55.719
This carriage,

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:57.760
even on the bumpiest of roads,

00:01:57.920 --> 00:01:59.040
will glide along perfectly smoothly.

00:01:59.840 --> 00:02:00.760
And this horse,

00:02:00.840 --> 00:02:02.319
my father bought it for a fortune.

00:02:02.799 --> 00:02:04.000
Apparently, during the Immortal Descent,

00:02:04.120 --> 00:02:05.760
it happened to absorb a bit of Celestial Power.

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:07.719
So even traveling a thousand miles a day,

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:08.800
it won't feel tired at all.

00:02:09.439 --> 00:02:10.120
As for me,

00:02:10.280 --> 00:02:12.120
I learned to drive a carriage yesterday.

00:02:12.680 --> 00:02:13.360
First of all,

00:02:14.159 --> 00:02:15.280
thanks for the carriage.

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:17.199
Secondly,

00:02:17.840 --> 00:02:19.759
why did you stand outside my door all night?

00:02:19.879 --> 00:02:20.639
I figured

00:02:20.840 --> 00:02:22.840
this would better show my sincerity,

00:02:23.280 --> 00:02:24.639
and prove to you, Senior Brother,

00:02:24.639 --> 00:02:25.719
how steadfast I am toward the Tao.

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:29.319
The guy's a bit of a fool,

00:02:29.879 --> 00:02:31.199
but the carriage is decent.

00:02:34.120 --> 00:02:35.080
This carriage

00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:37.039
is more than enough to show your sincerity.

00:02:38.159 --> 00:02:38.759
Let's go.

00:02:40.439 --> 00:02:41.000
Come on.

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:51.000
Wait, hold on.

00:02:51.919 --> 00:02:53.120
Your family's so rich,

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:54.680
why are you driving the carriage yourself?

00:02:55.639 --> 00:02:57.520
You've reached the point to enjoy life.

00:02:57.800 --> 00:02:58.599
But I

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:00.479
still need to endure much more hardship.

00:03:00.639 --> 00:03:01.240
Forget it.

00:03:01.599 --> 00:03:02.199
Suit yourself.

00:03:02.919 --> 00:03:03.840
Hey, brother,

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:05.960
if you're tired, I can take over.

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:07.680
Tired?

00:03:08.439 --> 00:03:10.599
Did Senior Brother send her to test my willpower?

00:03:11.439 --> 00:03:12.800
How could I possibly be tired?

00:03:13.879 --> 00:03:15.520
Under my onslaught of wealth,

00:03:15.879 --> 00:03:17.719
Senior Brother will only be corrupted.

00:03:17.879 --> 00:03:18.639
Meanwhile, I

00:03:18.919 --> 00:03:20.400
keep enduring hardship,

00:03:20.639 --> 00:03:21.639
growing stronger and stronger.

00:03:22.280 --> 00:03:23.199
Sooner or later,

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:25.159
I'll become the new Head Senior Brother

00:03:25.479 --> 00:03:27.080
and bring great glory to our sect.

00:03:27.680 --> 00:03:29.520
Destination: Imperial Capital. Move out!

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:30.240
Let's go!

00:03:30.439 --> 00:03:30.719
Hyah!

00:03:57.639 --> 00:03:58.719
Welcome to Windsnow City.

00:04:02.840 --> 00:04:04.800
Great, great.

00:04:06.680 --> 00:04:07.280
Wonderful.

00:04:11.400 --> 00:04:13.319
Great, great.

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:14.599
Excuse me.

00:04:14.599 --> 00:04:15.759
Great, great.

00:04:17.319 --> 00:04:19.879
One, two, three.

00:04:21.240 --> 00:04:22.959
Starlight City's fate this time

00:04:23.040 --> 00:04:24.040
rests in your hands.

00:04:29.160 --> 00:04:29.839
Tongtong.

00:04:30.079 --> 00:04:30.959
Look at that mountain.

00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:33.240
Uncle Xu.

00:04:33.800 --> 00:04:34.959
Our advertising spots

00:04:35.160 --> 00:04:36.600
are truly the most unique,

00:04:36.759 --> 00:04:37.680
the most eye-catching,

00:04:37.759 --> 00:04:38.600
the most direct,

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:40.120
and exceptionally advantageous.

00:04:40.319 --> 00:04:41.000
When the time comes,

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:43.000
their competition uniforms

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:44.879
will all carry your ads.

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:46.199
Our exclusive vehicles

00:04:46.279 --> 00:04:48.279
will also be filled with your ads.

00:04:48.720 --> 00:04:50.639
We can fully customize them for you.

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:52.279
To be honest with you,

00:04:53.040 --> 00:04:53.879
if my phone

00:04:53.879 --> 00:04:55.560
weren't on silent right now,

00:04:55.639 --> 00:04:57.319
it'd be ringing off the hook.

00:04:57.800 --> 00:04:58.399
So, you see,

00:04:58.879 --> 00:05:00.480
the time and ad spots left for you

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:02.160
are running out fast.

00:05:02.360 --> 00:05:02.920
Alright.

00:05:04.040 --> 00:05:05.240
Then the ad spots

00:05:05.759 --> 00:05:06.959
I'll leave to Young Master Liu.

00:05:07.560 --> 00:05:08.439
Of course, of course.

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:10.839
I'll definitely find you a prime spot.

00:06:00.600 --> 00:06:01.199
Young Master Liu.

00:06:12.959 --> 00:06:13.759
Destination:

00:06:14.720 --> 00:06:15.680
Imperial Capital.

00:06:16.319 --> 00:06:17.000
Let's go.

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:30.720
Word on the street is

00:06:30.879 --> 00:06:33.040
that we Springgrass City folk are weak,

00:06:33.160 --> 00:06:34.000
unfit for anything serious.

00:06:35.040 --> 00:06:36.160
But I believe

00:06:36.360 --> 00:06:37.319
this competition

00:06:37.519 --> 00:06:39.959
is our best chance to prove ourselves.

00:06:46.759 --> 00:06:47.560
In this contest,

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:48.879
our goal

00:06:49.199 --> 00:06:50.399
is first place, nothing less.

00:06:53.959 --> 00:06:54.560
Cheers!

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:56.839
Cheers!

00:06:57.199 --> 00:06:58.439
Cheers, cheers!

00:07:00.680 --> 00:07:02.360
Such boring men.

00:07:03.399 --> 00:07:05.480
Shouting that they're not cowards,

00:07:05.839 --> 00:07:08.199
yet making a hooker like me the captain.

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:09.959
Despising me in their hearts,

00:07:10.199 --> 00:07:11.639
yet lusting after me deep down.

00:07:15.439 --> 00:07:17.319
Who builds a Taoist temple this high?

00:07:17.680 --> 00:07:18.480
I'm exhausted.

00:07:20.560 --> 00:07:22.079
Slow, slow, slow down.

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:27.959
Be steadier next time.

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:28.720
That was way too bumpy.

00:07:30.839 --> 00:07:31.639
You knew I was coming?

00:07:31.639 --> 00:07:32.600
I heard the noise.

00:07:35.079 --> 00:07:35.959
The way you look,

00:07:36.079 --> 00:07:37.720
you don't really look like a Taoist.

00:07:40.399 --> 00:07:42.879
Why must a Taoist look like a Taoist?

00:07:43.360 --> 00:07:44.000
Fair enough.

00:07:44.920 --> 00:07:47.319
But in my mind,

00:07:47.399 --> 00:07:49.920
you Taoists are all plain

00:07:50.160 --> 00:07:50.959
and gaunt.

00:07:51.439 --> 00:07:53.759
Why live up to others' expectations?

00:07:53.879 --> 00:07:55.319
Whether I'm dressed in gold and silver

00:07:55.319 --> 00:07:56.680
or skin and bones,

00:07:56.920 --> 00:07:57.959
I'm still me.

00:07:58.000 --> 00:08:00.000
Spiritual Cultivation means zero desires.

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:01.240
So by what you're saying,

00:08:01.519 --> 00:08:02.519
in this competition,

00:08:02.519 --> 00:08:04.240
Autumnwater City won't fight for first?

00:08:04.639 --> 00:08:06.319
Spiritual Cultivation and wanting first,

00:08:06.439 --> 00:08:07.959
what's the necessary connection?

00:08:08.680 --> 00:08:10.199
Aren't you free of desires?

00:08:10.199 --> 00:08:11.680
The Tao is free of desires.

00:08:12.000 --> 00:08:14.240
Spiritual Cultivation is for immortality.

00:08:14.399 --> 00:08:15.759
So I do have desires.

00:08:16.199 --> 00:08:17.000
Since we're going,

00:08:17.079 --> 00:08:18.279
naturally we'll fight for first.

00:08:20.399 --> 00:08:22.399
You really are the most unusual

00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:24.480
Taoist I've ever met.

00:08:24.720 --> 00:08:25.560
Thanks for the compliment.

00:08:26.120 --> 00:08:28.600
No need to ask your elders before leaving?

00:08:28.759 --> 00:08:30.199
Yesterday I would've had to.

00:08:30.639 --> 00:08:32.440
But now I don't.

00:08:58.000 --> 00:08:59.320
Can't we rest a bit longer?

00:09:00.399 --> 00:09:01.200
Keep up, keep up.

00:09:01.200 --> 00:09:01.759
Yes.

00:09:36.279 --> 00:09:37.000
Just as I thought.

00:09:37.840 --> 00:09:39.759
Same location recorded in the ancestral text.

00:09:48.559 --> 00:09:50.480
Another lifesaver for next time.

00:09:53.240 --> 00:09:54.080
Wait, that's not right.

00:09:55.879 --> 00:09:57.879
I'm supposed to use this thing

00:09:58.600 --> 00:09:59.840
to boost my own strength

00:09:59.840 --> 00:10:01.960
and take Liu Chengfeng's life.

00:10:08.600 --> 00:10:09.840
Second Immortal Descent.

00:10:10.039 --> 00:10:12.399
Immortal Burial Grounds speed cultivation.

00:10:19.279 --> 00:10:20.480
So this is what the ancestors called

00:10:21.600 --> 00:10:22.799
listening to the Immortals' voice.

00:10:23.960 --> 00:10:25.279
Second Immortal Descent.

00:10:26.679 --> 00:10:27.559
Immortal Burial.

00:10:40.399 --> 00:10:41.399
Wang Qiusheng.

00:10:44.480 --> 00:10:45.440
Stop casting.

00:10:46.879 --> 00:10:47.840
Shi San's ability

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:49.519
lets him cause anyone

00:10:49.519 --> 00:10:50.720
with a Divine Blessing within 100 meters

00:10:51.039 --> 00:10:52.200
to lose their awakened skill.

00:10:56.639 --> 00:10:57.600
Wang Qiusheng,

00:10:58.519 --> 00:10:59.519
native of Shanhai City,

00:11:00.120 --> 00:11:01.399
once summoned the Rat Immortal,

00:11:01.679 --> 00:11:03.759
fled the manhunt to the Imperial Capital.

00:11:04.679 --> 00:11:05.720
Did I get that right?

00:11:06.879 --> 00:11:07.720
Who the hell are you?

00:11:08.039 --> 00:11:08.840
Ability:

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:10.480
suspected shadow-traveling.

00:11:10.559 --> 00:11:11.240
Right?

00:11:13.919 --> 00:11:15.519
I have no idea what you're talking about.

00:11:18.480 --> 00:11:19.279
San Gou.

00:11:31.240 --> 00:11:33.440
You've already wasted enough of my time.

00:11:33.759 --> 00:11:34.720
From here on out,

00:11:35.080 --> 00:11:37.279
I want you to answer only my questions.

00:11:39.320 --> 00:11:40.000
I...

00:11:41.000 --> 00:11:41.639
I...

00:11:42.360 --> 00:11:43.440
I'm Wang Qiusheng.

00:11:45.320 --> 00:11:46.600
You can summon Immortals.

00:11:49.559 --> 00:11:50.120
Yes.

00:11:50.279 --> 00:11:51.080
Yes, yes.

00:11:51.159 --> 00:11:52.639
It's the Wang family's ancestral art.

00:11:52.759 --> 00:11:54.840
But with today's level of Celestial Power,

00:11:55.279 --> 00:11:56.080
in the short term,

00:11:56.360 --> 00:11:57.840
I can't summon a second Immortal.

00:11:59.000 --> 00:12:00.159
Even if I forced it,

00:12:00.480 --> 00:12:02.200
it... it wouldn't top the Rat.

00:12:02.840 --> 00:12:04.080
Don't tell me what I didn't ask.

00:12:06.720 --> 00:12:08.000
How long till the next Immortal summoning?

00:12:08.159 --> 00:12:08.879
A month.

00:12:09.399 --> 00:12:10.399
A month will do.

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:15.279
Looks like

00:12:15.919 --> 00:12:17.879
you're not hurt that badly after all.

00:12:28.879 --> 00:12:30.639
Don't leave the Imperial Capital for now.

00:12:31.320 --> 00:12:32.960
Wait for my orders at all times.

00:12:33.919 --> 00:12:35.320
Get any funny ideas,

00:12:36.600 --> 00:12:37.480
and you're dead.

00:12:47.919 --> 00:12:49.000
Why haven't you left yet?

00:12:49.559 --> 00:12:50.200
Go.

00:12:50.600 --> 00:12:51.240
Go.

00:12:58.320 --> 00:12:59.039
San Gou.

00:12:59.879 --> 00:13:01.240
Was he lying just now?

00:13:01.879 --> 00:13:02.519
No.

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:04.279
He's just frightened,

00:13:04.440 --> 00:13:05.639
so his elevated heart rate is normal.

00:13:05.919 --> 00:13:07.240
Master Gou's move just now

00:13:07.519 --> 00:13:09.279
was so sharp and decisive.

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:10.720
Compared to your forbidden arts,

00:13:10.919 --> 00:13:11.799
it's nothing worth mentioning.

00:13:12.039 --> 00:13:13.360
Those without a Divine Blessing

00:13:14.440 --> 00:13:16.120
will be left behind by this era.

00:13:18.120 --> 00:13:20.240
I've never believed in heavenly gifts.

00:13:20.639 --> 00:13:21.639
Compared to that,

00:13:22.080 --> 00:13:23.440
I trust myself more.

00:13:24.320 --> 00:13:26.240
When Wang Qiusheng summons an Immortal,

00:13:26.840 --> 00:13:28.759
we can absolutely have that Immortal

00:13:28.840 --> 00:13:30.600
grant you a Divine Blessing to your face.

00:13:31.279 --> 00:13:31.960
That way,

00:13:32.519 --> 00:13:33.720
it'd be the most interesting.

00:13:35.240 --> 00:13:35.919
Thank you, Young Master Gu.

00:13:36.720 --> 00:13:39.120
The legendary top thief surrendering willingly,

00:13:40.039 --> 00:13:40.759
the Divine Blessing

00:13:41.320 --> 00:13:42.240
is well-deserved.

00:13:46.120 --> 00:13:46.799
Do me a favor.

00:13:47.720 --> 00:13:49.519
Keep an eye on my brother for me.

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:51.200
He works himself ragged day and night.

00:13:51.799 --> 00:13:53.799
If he happened to drop dead in his office,

00:13:54.360 --> 00:13:55.440
that wouldn't be good.

00:14:02.600 --> 00:14:04.200
The legendary top thief,

00:14:04.720 --> 00:14:06.399
I believe once he gets a Divine Blessing,

00:14:06.759 --> 00:14:08.080
his power will surge even more.

00:14:08.279 --> 00:14:09.480
Congratulations in advance

00:14:09.639 --> 00:14:10.919
on gaining a fierce warrior.

00:14:11.799 --> 00:14:12.600
Who said

00:14:13.159 --> 00:14:14.440
he was getting the Divine Blessing?

00:14:14.919 --> 00:14:16.120
In this era,

00:14:16.639 --> 00:14:17.480
A master thief...

00:14:18.039 --> 00:14:18.960
what use is he?

00:14:18.960 --> 00:14:20.480
Even a beggar,

00:14:20.879 --> 00:14:22.600
once given a Divine Blessing, would prove

00:14:22.679 --> 00:14:23.919
more useful than him.

00:14:24.600 --> 00:14:26.759
Why would I waste an Immortal's favor

00:14:27.039 --> 00:14:27.960
on someone like him?

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:29.919
A master thief.

00:14:32.039 --> 00:14:33.279
Then why keep him around?

00:14:33.600 --> 00:14:35.120
Is he still useful for something?

00:14:35.519 --> 00:14:36.320
The competition,

00:14:36.919 --> 00:14:38.080
the award ceremony,

00:14:38.639 --> 00:14:40.080
the prize goes missing,

00:14:40.799 --> 00:14:42.039
and the culprit

00:14:42.759 --> 00:14:44.679
is the world's top thief himself.

00:14:45.960 --> 00:14:47.080
What a scene,

00:14:48.320 --> 00:14:49.399
how interesting it'd be.

00:14:54.039 --> 00:14:55.080
I'm a bit curious.

00:14:55.519 --> 00:14:56.879
You're clearly my brother's man,

00:14:57.200 --> 00:14:58.399
so why pledge yourself to me?

00:14:58.960 --> 00:15:00.080
He's impulsive,

00:15:00.200 --> 00:15:01.039
unscrupulous,

00:15:01.519 --> 00:15:02.200
and too foolish.

00:15:03.279 --> 00:15:05.159
I don't want his stupidity to kill me.

00:15:06.480 --> 00:15:07.360
That's reasonable.

00:15:08.399 --> 00:15:09.159
Tell me then,

00:15:09.240 --> 00:15:09.919
what do you want?

00:15:10.759 --> 00:15:11.720
A Divine Blessing.

00:15:16.320 --> 00:15:17.039
Deal.

00:15:17.600 --> 00:15:18.960
No need for an Immortal's Divine Blessing.

00:15:19.679 --> 00:15:20.639
The Vessel itself

00:15:20.799 --> 00:15:22.360
contains energy from an Immortal's body:

00:15:22.360 --> 00:15:23.799
a vast amount of Celestial Power.

00:15:24.000 --> 00:15:24.799
When the time comes,

00:15:26.120 --> 00:15:28.559
the Vessel from the finals will be yours.

00:15:29.200 --> 00:15:30.320
Wear it for a while,

00:15:30.799 --> 00:15:32.240
and naturally get a Divine Blessing.

00:15:32.639 --> 00:15:33.399
But what if

00:15:33.919 --> 00:15:35.320
the competitors cause trouble?

00:15:36.960 --> 00:15:39.440
The one who stole the prize is my brother,

00:15:39.600 --> 00:15:41.519
Gu Changye's man, Zhou San Gou.

00:15:42.200 --> 00:15:43.480
What does that have to do with my guard,

00:15:43.879 --> 00:15:45.559
the new recruit with a Divine Blessing,

00:15:45.559 --> 00:15:47.159
Zhou Sanxing?

00:15:48.799 --> 00:15:50.039
The one really in trouble

00:15:50.360 --> 00:15:51.720
is Gu Changye, isn't it?

00:15:57.879 --> 00:15:58.720
Alright, you may go.

00:16:07.039 --> 00:16:09.279
Once the world's top thief,

00:16:10.320 --> 00:16:11.159
and now...